<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="356" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,1084,1902]" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,308,1804,1830]" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">Remarks</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName authority="Viraktamath &amp; Yeshwanth, 2021" authorityName="Viraktamath &amp; Yeshwanth" authorityYear="2021" box="[324,515,1804,1830]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Macropsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="356" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dalhousiensis" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[324,515,1804,1830]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">M. dalhousiensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[525,616,1804,1830]" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[525,616,1804,1830]" pageId="3" pageNumber="356" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
externally resembles 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Viraktamath" authorityYear="1996" box="[867,1007,1804,1830]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Macropsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="356" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ganeshai">
<emphasis box="[867,1007,1804,1830]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">M. ganeshai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<emphasis box="[1066,1226,1804,1830]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Viraktamath" authorityYear="1996" box="[1066,1222,1804,1830]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Macropsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="356" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vagdeviae">M. vagdeviae</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
It differs from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Viraktamath" authorityYear="1996" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Macropsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="356" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ganeshai">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">M. ganeshai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the aedeagal shaft being narrowed apically compared to slightly broadened in lateral view beyond the dorsal curvature in the latter; from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Viraktamath" authorityYear="1996" box="[543,694,1876,1902]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Macropsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="356" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vagdeviae">
<emphasis box="[543,694,1876,1902]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">M. vagdeviae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
it differs in having much longer pygofer ventral process.
</paragraph>
